1
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,360
"Ashes of Love"

2
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,240
"Episode 38"

3
00:02:51,100 --> 00:02:52,040
Liu Ying.

4
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:54,180
Jin Mi, please do me a favor.

5
00:03:13,300 --> 00:03:15,720
Now that you’ve borrowed Beast of Dreams

6
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:16,900
from Immortal Jin Mi,

7
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:18,940
just use it.

8
00:03:19,140 --> 00:03:19,800
Don’t hesitate.

9
00:03:21,740 --> 00:03:25,080
I’m just a little afraid of seeing the past of Mu Ci.

10
00:03:25,820 --> 00:03:27,360
I’ll be with you.

11
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,900
Your Majesty.

12
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:56,480
Is everything fine with Sui He and Xu Feng?

13
00:03:56,820 --> 00:03:57,620
Your Majesty,

14
00:03:57,900 --> 00:03:59,120
both of them are fine.

15
00:03:59,480 --> 00:04:00,920
They were born in the mortal world safely.

16
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:04,120
Restore Sui He’s memory immediately,

17
00:04:04,700 --> 00:04:07,920
so they can cultivate feelings in this period.

18
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,020
Yes.

19
00:04:09,580 --> 00:04:10,760
How about Jin Mi?

20
00:04:11,300 --> 00:04:12,860
As His Majesty sent Fairy Yuan Ji

21
00:04:13,060 --> 00:04:14,140
to guard her all day long,

22
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:16,580
I have no chance to kill her.

23
00:04:17,060 --> 00:04:17,660
All right.

24
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,580
Try a few days later,

25
00:04:20,180 --> 00:04:22,960
lest His Majesty will have something on me.

26
00:04:23,700 --> 00:04:24,480
I see.

27
00:04:25,420 --> 00:04:27,900
Is your Spirit-Vanishing Arrow ready?

28
00:04:28,660 --> 00:04:29,440
Your Majesty,

29
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:32,780
as the Spirit-Vanishing Arrow
is made with my bones and blood,

30
00:04:32,900 --> 00:04:34,020
it’ll take more time.

31
00:04:34,340 --> 00:04:36,540
Please give me a few more days, Your Majesty.

32
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,780
OK.

33
00:04:39,260 --> 00:04:40,720
I’ll give you a few more days.

34
00:04:40,860 --> 00:04:41,800
Thank you.

35
00:06:02,540 --> 00:06:03,740
Do you still love me?

36
00:06:04,300 --> 00:06:05,080
Yes.

37
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:07,380
I’ve always loved you

38
00:06:08,420 --> 00:06:09,520
and loved you for a long time.

39
00:06:24,540 --> 00:06:25,840
However, I’ve already been in love with others.

40
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:28,160
As you’re neither an immortal nor a demon,

41
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:30,560
I can’t be with you.

42
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,520
How silly you are!

43
00:06:44,260 --> 00:06:48,420
I’ve always just loved you
from the beginning to the end.

44
00:06:54,700 --> 00:06:57,500
I didn’t expect that Her Majesty controlled Mu Ci.

45
00:06:59,620 --> 00:07:00,860
She wants to hurt Jin Mi.

46
00:07:01,820 --> 00:07:02,260
No.

47
00:07:03,220 --> 00:07:04,720
We must tell Jin Mi about that

48
00:07:05,500 --> 00:07:07,180
and ask her to be on guard of Her Majesty.

49
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:12,660
"Sweet Spring"

50
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:14,240
Jin Mi,

51
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:16,540
thanks for lending me Beast of Dreams.

52
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:18,780
You’re welcome.

53
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:22,280
If it hadn’t been for your full help
in the mortal world,

54
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:23,900
I would have been vanished

55
00:07:24,340 --> 00:07:25,640
like Rou Rou.

56
00:07:28,080 --> 00:07:29,160
I wonder whether Beast of Dreams

57
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:31,000
is of help to your old friend.

58
00:07:33,140 --> 00:07:35,300
Jin Mi, to tell you the truth,

59
00:07:36,100 --> 00:07:39,520
the one who killed Qiang Huo
with Spirit-Vanishing Arrow

60
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:41,900
that day was my old friend.

61
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:48,300
He is Mu Ci

62
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,900
who was kind originally.

63
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:52,680
He had to hurt you
as he was in others’ control.

64
00:07:53,380 --> 00:07:54,660
If you can’t forgive him,

65
00:07:54,780 --> 00:07:56,280
get even with me.

66
00:07:56,860 --> 00:07:57,780
Whatever you want to do,

67
00:07:58,660 --> 00:08:00,000
I’ll bear it for him.

68
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:10,500
Stand up first.

69
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:23,760
Who controls your friend?

70
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:25,000
Her Majesty.

71
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,240
Her Majesty?

72
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:28,680
I don’t know why she wants to hurt you.

73
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,580
It’s better you’re in the Floral Realm now.

74
00:08:30,960 --> 00:08:32,360
If you go back to the Heaven Realm some day,

75
00:08:32,800 --> 00:08:33,800
be careful.

76
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,380
My Lord

77
00:08:44,660 --> 00:08:46,680
the absorbing power of the
Autopsy Wild Silkworms is so strong.

78
00:08:47,860 --> 00:08:48,680
In fact,

79
00:08:49,300 --> 00:08:51,060
there is a way to control

80
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:52,340
the Autopsy Wild Silkworms

81
00:08:52,500 --> 00:08:54,000
from absorbing his magic power.

82
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,960
I raised him from his childhood,

83
00:08:57,280 --> 00:08:58,420
so my feelings for him

84
00:08:58,560 --> 00:09:00,540
are no less than those of Liu Ying for him.

85
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:03,500
I can’t bear to see him so painful either.

86
00:09:04,140 --> 00:09:05,040
My Lord

87
00:09:05,340 --> 00:09:06,980
I know your mind.

88
00:09:07,620 --> 00:09:10,580
But the way to control
the Autopsy Wild Silkworms is...

89
00:09:14,020 --> 00:09:14,560
Father

90
00:09:15,420 --> 00:09:17,780
what should we do to control
the Autopsy Wild Silkworms?

91
00:09:26,620 --> 00:09:29,200
Liu Ying, you’d better know nothing

92
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,400
about the way to save him.

93
00:09:30,900 --> 00:09:31,640
Why?

94
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:32,760
Because it costs much magic power

95
00:09:32,860 --> 00:09:34,720
of the one who saves him.

96
00:09:35,100 --> 00:09:35,800
I know

97
00:09:36,020 --> 00:09:36,860
you’ll sacrifice yourself

98
00:09:36,900 --> 00:09:38,520
to save him.

99
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:40,300
However, I hate to see that.

100
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:41,220
Father.

101
00:09:43,900 --> 00:09:44,580
No.

102
00:09:45,300 --> 00:09:46,100
I don’t want.

103
00:09:56,180 --> 00:09:56,860
Liu Ying,

104
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,180
stop.

105
00:10:00,820 --> 00:10:02,100
Stop now.

106
00:10:02,180 --> 00:10:03,160
Take your hand off.

107
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,240
I’ll save him.

108
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:06,460
I won’t live alone if he dies.

109
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:09,540
Silly girl, you’ll make him more painful

110
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:11,380
by forcibly transferring magic power to him.

111
00:10:15,160 --> 00:10:15,740
Father,

112
00:10:16,380 --> 00:10:17,780
what should I do to save him?

113
00:10:27,620 --> 00:10:28,180
Father,

114
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,520
what are you doing?

115
00:10:30,140 --> 00:10:31,280
Help him to get up now.

116
00:10:33,620 --> 00:10:36,840
Originally, Autopsy Wild Silkworms are unsolvable.

117
00:10:38,060 --> 00:10:40,340
However, the bones and blood
of those with strong magic power

118
00:10:40,580 --> 00:10:43,240
can suppress the Autopsy Wild Silkworms in his body

119
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,460
and ease his pain for a while.

120
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:51,860
However, as the one saving him
loses his bones and blood,

121
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:54,280
his magic power will decrease immediately

122
00:10:54,460 --> 00:10:56,420
and he will feel very tired.

123
00:10:57,060 --> 00:10:59,240
I didn’t want you to try it before,

124
00:10:59,860 --> 00:11:02,720
because I feared that you couldn’t bear it.

125
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,220
Father.

126
00:11:05,300 --> 00:11:09,940
I raised him since his childhood.

127
00:11:12,900 --> 00:11:15,680
I know you like him sincerely

128
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:20,720
and just want you to be happy.

129
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:22,960
Father,

130
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:25,220
I’m sorry.

131
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:34,660
I know

132
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:36,580
when Xu Feng was grounded,

133
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:39,100
Jin Mi went to the Qiwu Palace secretly.

134
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:41,180
As we couldn’t kill

135
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,940
the little fairy in the mortal world,

136
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:45,220
the feelings between them

137
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:46,920
have been deeper now.

138
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:48,960
If you had tried hard,

139
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:50,400
it wouldn’t be so.

140
00:11:51,280 --> 00:11:53,100
I’m sorry to fail you.

141
00:11:55,380 --> 00:11:56,660
Fine. Sit down.

142
00:12:03,220 --> 00:12:04,480
Run Yu

143
00:12:04,900 --> 00:12:06,180
always pretends to be

144
00:12:06,640 --> 00:12:09,500
gentle and harmless before others.

145
00:12:09,820 --> 00:12:11,180
However, no one knows

146
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:12,800
what he thinks.

147
00:12:13,260 --> 00:12:14,960
He showed his true self

148
00:12:15,100 --> 00:12:16,540
by the Dongting Lake back then.

149
00:12:17,040 --> 00:12:18,100
I don’t believe that

150
00:12:18,520 --> 00:12:20,160
he doesn’t want to be Heavenly Emperor.

151
00:12:20,940 --> 00:12:22,860
Once he gets married with Jin Mi,

152
00:12:23,300 --> 00:12:24,800
Water Immortal, Wind Immortal

153
00:12:24,980 --> 00:12:25,840
and the Floral Realm

154
00:12:26,060 --> 00:12:27,320
will be his power.

155
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:30,460
If Xu Feng is still

156
00:12:30,520 --> 00:12:31,720
obsessed with Jin Mi,

157
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:34,260
there’ll be a terrible result.

158
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:39,300
All in all, Jin Mi is the biggest obstacle.

159
00:12:39,680 --> 00:12:41,620
Now the only way is

160
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:43,840
to eliminate her.

161
00:12:44,220 --> 00:12:46,300
So Xu Feng will forget her

162
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:47,920
and Run Yu’s support will be lost.

163
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:51,060
However, I’m afraid it is difficult to kill her

164
00:12:51,060 --> 00:12:54,200
in both the Floral Realm and the Heaven Realm.

165
00:12:54,700 --> 00:12:55,820
As long as I want to,

166
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:58,920
I can do anything in the world.

167
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,700
Mi has been to the Qiwu Palace twice.

168
00:13:06,860 --> 00:13:08,040
What do you think?

169
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:11,600
I got her back with great efforts.

170
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:14,320
Originally, I want her to be carefree.

171
00:13:14,760 --> 00:13:17,200
It’s fine if she likes Night Immortal

172
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:19,740
who is in harmony with the rest of the world,

173
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:22,200
so the whole family can
have a free and unfettered life.

174
00:13:23,060 --> 00:13:28,340
Unexpectedly, she falls in love with Fire Immortal.

175
00:13:28,940 --> 00:13:30,600
I don’t care about the criticism of the Heaven Realm.

176
00:13:30,940 --> 00:13:31,960
What matters is that

177
00:13:32,420 --> 00:13:34,460
Her Majesty won’t be good to her.

178
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:36,360
Absolutely, we can’t

179
00:13:36,860 --> 00:13:38,860
remain indifferent to her matter.

180
00:13:39,180 --> 00:13:40,280
Her Majesty

181
00:13:40,660 --> 00:13:42,540
won’t just let us go.

182
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:45,200
Our quiet life

183
00:13:47,420 --> 00:13:48,800
will end.

184
00:13:49,760 --> 00:13:51,700
I don’t care whether we can lead a free life

185
00:13:52,460 --> 00:13:56,320
or have to fight against Her Majesty.

186
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:58,460
I just wish Mi a happy life.

187
00:13:59,460 --> 00:14:00,760
However, it is really terrible as I think of

188
00:14:01,300 --> 00:14:02,720
her experience in the mortal world.

189
00:14:03,020 --> 00:14:05,380
If she insists on staying with Fire Immortal,

190
00:14:06,020 --> 00:14:07,840
I wonder Her Majesty must figure out some tricks

191
00:14:07,880 --> 00:14:08,740
to hurt her.

192
00:14:09,900 --> 00:14:12,120
I’m afraid it is difficult to guard against her.

193
00:14:12,640 --> 00:14:13,700
I’ll find a chance

194
00:14:14,100 --> 00:14:15,800
to make it clear to His Majesty.

195
00:14:16,400 --> 00:14:17,540
What a wishful thinking!

196
00:14:18,760 --> 00:14:20,960
Haven’t you seen the way he treats her

197
00:14:21,440 --> 00:14:23,440
after Su Li’s death?

198
00:14:24,260 --> 00:14:25,360
Don’t expect anything.

199
00:14:43,860 --> 00:14:46,100
At first, I wanted to maker them happy.

200
00:14:47,160 --> 00:14:49,620
Unexpectedly, Daddy and Auntie Lin Xiu

201
00:14:49,740 --> 00:14:51,180
are worrying about me.

202
00:14:52,800 --> 00:14:53,860
As his daughter,

203
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:55,780
I care nothing but my love.

204
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,020
Phoenix.

205
00:14:59,620 --> 00:15:02,040
Now only the secret behind the veil

206
00:15:02,540 --> 00:15:03,780
can make my emotions fluctuant

207
00:15:04,160 --> 00:15:06,140
and make me be lost in a reverie.

208
00:15:07,500 --> 00:15:08,640
How can

209
00:15:08,780 --> 00:15:10,360
you do that?

210
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:25,560
In the mortal world, you promised to marry me.

211
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:27,140
Will you keep your promise?

212
00:15:27,920 --> 00:15:29,660
I’ll explain to Daddy

213
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:31,280
and ask him to break off my engagement.

214
00:15:31,340 --> 00:15:33,560
By that time, I’ll keep my promise.

215
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:46,960
Why is it so strange in my heart all these days?

216
00:15:48,560 --> 00:15:50,740
Is everything between Phoenix
and me in the mortal world

217
00:15:51,060 --> 00:15:53,920
just impulsiveness in a flash?

218
00:15:55,260 --> 00:15:57,980
It’s really like a dream to me now.

219
00:15:59,020 --> 00:16:01,680
If Her Majesty really killed Rou Rou,

220
00:16:02,340 --> 00:16:04,540
she will be my enemy

221
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:06,900
and Phoenix is my enemy’s son.

222
00:16:07,760 --> 00:16:09,660
How should I face him?

223
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:12,380
She killed Rou Rou.

224
00:16:13,220 --> 00:16:16,380
Daddy and Auntie Lin Xiu
are worried about me.

225
00:16:16,820 --> 00:16:19,300
If I insist on staying with Phoenix,

226
00:16:19,900 --> 00:16:21,800
I will let them down.

227
00:16:22,940 --> 00:16:23,540
Daddy,

228
00:16:24,040 --> 00:16:25,180
when did you come here?

229
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:27,720
You even didn’t notice that I was here.

230
00:16:28,760 --> 00:16:31,160
Are you worrying about
your engagement with Night Immortal?

231
00:16:32,520 --> 00:16:33,900
Marriage isn’t trivial.

232
00:16:34,340 --> 00:16:36,540
If you really destroy the
engagement with Night immortal,

233
00:16:36,820 --> 00:16:38,700
many people will be embarrassed.

234
00:16:45,180 --> 00:16:45,760
Daddy,

235
00:16:46,740 --> 00:16:47,900
my engagement...

236
00:16:52,940 --> 00:16:54,000
My engagement

237
00:16:54,740 --> 00:16:56,100
will be decided by you.

238
00:16:57,260 --> 00:16:59,160
I was so willful before.

239
00:17:01,300 --> 00:17:02,740
I don’t know why.

240
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:05,180
You’re so childish

241
00:17:05,580 --> 00:17:06,800
that you always do whatever you like.

242
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:08,920
Do you really think it clearly now?

243
00:17:09,040 --> 00:17:10,860
Or will you change your mind tomorrow?

244
00:17:12,320 --> 00:17:13,140
I’ve made up my mind

245
00:17:13,540 --> 00:17:14,620
and won’t change any more.

246
00:17:16,500 --> 00:17:17,940
Unexpectedly, both sons of His Majesty

247
00:17:18,740 --> 00:17:21,100
would be chosen by you at will.

248
00:17:22,180 --> 00:17:23,720
The wedding date is approaching.

249
00:17:23,800 --> 00:17:25,780
If you have made a choice,

250
00:17:25,860 --> 00:17:27,000
don’t regret it.

251
00:17:30,840 --> 00:17:32,100
Have you really made up your mind?

252
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:39,760
Yes.

253
00:17:40,660 --> 00:17:41,660
I won’t change any more.

254
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:44,300
There are complex rituals
for the wedding in Heaven Realm.

255
00:17:45,280 --> 00:17:47,820
Stay with me in the Luoxiang Mansion
for a few days,

256
00:17:48,200 --> 00:17:50,400
so Auntie Lin Xiu can teach you
the rituals in the Heaven Realm.

257
00:17:50,900 --> 00:17:52,680
You are used to being free in the Floral Realm.

258
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:55,320
If you make any mistakes by then,

259
00:17:55,380 --> 00:17:57,120
you’ll disgrace Night Immortal.

260
00:17:58,060 --> 00:18:00,920
I think you’re afraid that I will disgrace you.

261
00:18:03,060 --> 00:18:04,760
Even so,

262
00:18:06,380 --> 00:18:08,320
that’s my honor as your daddy.

263
00:18:18,740 --> 00:18:20,060
What’s going on with Mother recently?

264
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:22,640
Her Majesty hasn’t left
the Zifangyun Palace recently.

265
00:18:22,980 --> 00:18:23,840
However, Princess Sui He

266
00:18:24,020 --> 00:18:25,820
has often visited the Zifangyun Palace recently.

267
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:29,440
Continue keeping an eye on Mother.

268
00:18:30,600 --> 00:18:31,480
By the way, Your Highness,

269
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:33,820
I heard that today Immortal Jin Mi
will come to the Heaven Realm

270
00:18:34,260 --> 00:18:35,840
and stay in the Luoxiang Mansion
of Water Immortal.

271
00:18:36,500 --> 00:18:37,100
Really?

272
00:18:39,580 --> 00:18:41,080
Are you going to the Empyrean Cloud Palace?

273
00:18:41,140 --> 00:18:42,080
Go to the Luoxiang Mansion.

274
00:18:42,460 --> 00:18:44,900
His Majesty invited Xuan Ling Lord Doumu

275
00:18:44,940 --> 00:18:46,420
to discuss Chan in the Empyrean Cloud Palace.

276
00:18:49,060 --> 00:18:49,900
I know.

277
00:18:50,100 --> 00:18:50,860
I have a sense.

