00:19:01,660 --> 00:19:02,860
Immortal Jin Mi,

279
00:19:02,900 --> 00:19:04,360
Fire Immortal is asking to see you outside.

280
00:19:06,020 --> 00:19:06,780
No.

281
00:19:07,280 --> 00:19:09,780
Tell him to go back.

282
00:19:10,460 --> 00:19:11,020
Yes.

283
00:19:29,900 --> 00:19:30,860
Your Highness,

284
00:19:31,120 --> 00:19:32,780
Immortal Jin Mi won’t meet you.

285
00:19:33,100 --> 00:19:34,200
Please go back.

286
00:19:35,380 --> 00:19:36,600
What’s wrong with her?

287
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:39,760
Your Highness, you...

288
00:19:53,040 --> 00:19:54,540
Why do you refuse to see me today?

289
00:19:56,640 --> 00:19:57,600
Besides today,

290
00:19:58,280 --> 00:19:59,500
Your Highness,

291
00:20:00,280 --> 00:20:01,780
we’d better not meet each other afterwards.

292
00:20:03,540 --> 00:20:05,740
I’ll marry Night Immortal in the end.

293
00:20:06,380 --> 00:20:07,300
What?

294
00:20:08,960 --> 00:20:10,480
When we are together,

295
00:20:10,880 --> 00:20:11,920
my daddy,

296
00:20:12,340 --> 00:20:13,400
Auntie Lin Xiu,

297
00:20:13,920 --> 00:20:15,000
His Majesty,

298
00:20:15,020 --> 00:20:15,980
Chief Peony

299
00:20:15,980 --> 00:20:17,360
and Night Immortal are all worried.

300
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:19,320
Such an worrying matter

301
00:20:19,820 --> 00:20:21,060
must be wrong.

302
00:20:21,440 --> 00:20:22,740
There is nothing wrong

303
00:20:23,140 --> 00:20:24,140
with love.

304
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:26,960
Jin Mi, you know my mind.

305
00:20:27,840 --> 00:20:29,300
What’s more, we love each other.

306
00:20:29,460 --> 00:20:30,320
Your Highness,

307
00:20:31,420 --> 00:20:33,080
we once did love each other.

308
00:20:34,240 --> 00:20:36,500
However, it was just the
impulsiveness of human beings.

309
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:37,800
As for the present,

310
00:20:38,120 --> 00:20:40,260
we can’t make it

311
00:20:41,060 --> 00:20:42,200
with our deep love alone.

312
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:45,300
I won’t allow you to marry Night Immortal.

313
00:20:46,300 --> 00:20:47,400
Do you know that

314
00:20:47,620 --> 00:20:48,980
there is a witness everywhere

315
00:20:49,260 --> 00:20:50,860
and the one destroying
others’ marriage will go to the hell?

316
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:51,840
Don’t you fear that?

317
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:52,800
I’m an immortal.

318
00:20:52,880 --> 00:20:53,980
I’m not afraid of going to the hell.

319
00:20:54,060 --> 00:20:55,140
I’m afraid of nothing

320
00:20:55,460 --> 00:20:57,120
in heaven and earth.

321
00:20:59,820 --> 00:21:01,600
The only thing I’m afraid of

322
00:21:03,220 --> 00:21:04,620
is your mind.

323
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:07,780
After experiencing hardships,

324
00:21:08,960 --> 00:21:10,180
you were willing to accept me,

325
00:21:10,260 --> 00:21:11,880
which made me really very happy.

326
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:15,840
In the past, I had no expectation for the future.

327
00:21:17,540 --> 00:21:19,120
But after meeting you,

328
00:21:19,900 --> 00:21:22,100
I have been looking forward
to our future every day.

329
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:24,580
However, today

330
00:21:25,480 --> 00:21:27,760
you even said our love was a mistake

331
00:21:28,440 --> 00:21:29,620
and wanted to marry Night Immortal.

332
00:21:30,700 --> 00:21:32,660
I don’t know why you change your mind suddenly.

333
00:21:34,200 --> 00:21:35,460
Has anyone forced you

334
00:21:35,860 --> 00:21:37,440
or have I done anything that made you awkward?

335
00:21:37,560 --> 00:21:38,840
Tell me and I’ll handle it.

336
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:39,380
Your Highness,

337
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:41,520
you’re making me awkward now.

338
00:21:45,700 --> 00:21:47,180
I don’t know what to do either.

339
00:21:49,760 --> 00:21:50,680
Your Highness,

340
00:21:52,720 --> 00:21:55,060
Lord Doumu will talk about Chan today.

341
00:21:55,240 --> 00:21:57,400
I think you’d better go earlier for it.

342
00:22:01,680 --> 00:22:03,400
I’ll pretend that you get
confused temporarily today.

343
00:22:05,920 --> 00:22:07,160
I’ll wait for you to figure it out.

344
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:22,060
The Heaven Realm is different
from the Floral Realm,

345
00:22:22,740 --> 00:22:24,020
so be careful.

346
00:22:26,300 --> 00:22:28,100
Especially, don’t get close to Mother.

347
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:49,400
Phoenix must know something.

348
00:22:54,720 --> 00:22:55,060
Your Highness.

349
00:23:04,900 --> 00:23:06,260
Keep watch on the Zifangyun Palace.

350
00:23:06,660 --> 00:23:08,920
Tell me in time whatever Her Majesty does.

351
00:23:09,300 --> 00:23:09,820
Yes.

352
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:26,000
Xu Feng.

353
00:23:26,120 --> 00:23:27,400
Xu Feng,

354
00:23:27,640 --> 00:23:30,000
as fairies in the Heaven Realm asked me,

355
00:23:30,040 --> 00:23:31,180
I connected you with these Red Strings.

356
00:23:32,060 --> 00:23:35,120
I know your only love is Jin Mi.

357
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:35,880
However,

358
00:23:36,800 --> 00:23:40,100
I just do so to get good luck.

359
00:23:40,220 --> 00:23:42,260
You were so cruel

360
00:23:42,360 --> 00:23:46,080
that you burned my innocent Red Strings.

361
00:23:48,480 --> 00:23:49,080
Xu Feng,

362
00:23:51,120 --> 00:23:53,060
you are so furious.

363
00:23:53,680 --> 00:23:54,880
Has anyone offended you?

364
00:23:59,820 --> 00:24:00,560
Uncle.

365
00:24:01,300 --> 00:24:02,300
Xu Feng.

366
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:03,520
Good boy.

367
00:24:08,360 --> 00:24:10,940
Xu Feng, the discussion will begin soon.

368
00:24:10,980 --> 00:24:12,620
Don’t stand still. Move now.

369
00:24:13,380 --> 00:24:14,740
Let’s go.

370
00:24:24,100 --> 00:24:25,000
Immortal Jin Mi.

371
00:24:26,800 --> 00:24:28,800
Why are you here today?

372
00:24:29,100 --> 00:24:30,900
Supreme Lord Lao will distribute elixir today.

373
00:24:31,040 --> 00:24:32,680
I come specially to invite Water Immortal to try it.

374
00:24:33,540 --> 00:24:34,540
What a pity!

375
00:24:34,720 --> 00:24:35,440
He has attended the discussion

376
00:24:35,500 --> 00:24:37,360
of Xuan Ling Lord Doumu

377
00:24:37,440 --> 00:24:38,420
and is not here today.

378
00:24:39,920 --> 00:24:41,880
No one will appreciate his elixir.

379
00:24:42,140 --> 00:24:43,740
I’m afraid Lord Lao will be disappointed.

380
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:46,000
Do you have time

381
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:47,400
to appreciate elixir in the mansion?

382
00:24:48,600 --> 00:24:49,140
Me?

383
00:24:50,220 --> 00:24:51,340
Is it appropriate for me to go there?

384
00:24:51,580 --> 00:24:54,080
I can account for failing to invite your father

385
00:24:54,360 --> 00:24:56,200
as I invite you.

386
00:25:06,600 --> 00:25:07,620
Leave first.

387
00:25:08,440 --> 00:25:09,420
Yes.

388
00:25:11,180 --> 00:25:13,160
It turns out that she is from the Zifangyun Palace.

389
00:25:13,220 --> 00:25:15,040
Is it Her Majesty?

390
00:25:16,260 --> 00:25:19,600
OK. Please wait for a while.

391
00:25:19,880 --> 00:25:21,060
I’ll go in to get changed.

392
00:25:21,320 --> 00:25:23,300
I’ll wait for you here.

393
00:25:35,860 --> 00:25:36,560
Mi,

394
00:25:37,520 --> 00:25:38,340
your practice of the Summoning Magic

395
00:25:38,340 --> 00:25:39,740
is getting better.

396
00:25:41,120 --> 00:25:42,060
Keep your voice down.

397
00:25:48,540 --> 00:25:49,440
Mi,

398
00:25:49,800 --> 00:25:50,760
are you so lonely

399
00:25:50,940 --> 00:25:52,660
as you haven’t got married with

400
00:25:52,920 --> 00:25:54,620
Night Immortal?

401
00:25:55,020 --> 00:25:55,680
So you want me...

402
00:25:55,720 --> 00:25:56,540
Stand up.

403
00:25:57,580 --> 00:25:58,740
I’m serious.

404
00:25:59,480 --> 00:26:02,080
Now go to the Empyrean Cloud Palace
for my daddy

405
00:26:02,420 --> 00:26:03,780
and tell him that

406
00:26:03,880 --> 00:26:05,720
Her Majesty sends someone to take me away.

407
00:26:05,860 --> 00:26:06,840
Her Majesty?

408
00:26:08,120 --> 00:26:09,780
The Fairchild outside said

409
00:26:09,980 --> 00:26:11,720
she was a fairy of Supreme Lord Lao

410
00:26:11,820 --> 00:26:13,580
and asked me to taste elixir in their mansion.

411
00:26:14,060 --> 00:26:15,700
However, she is from Her Majesty’s palace.

412
00:26:16,580 --> 00:26:19,020
Her Majesty is crafty and insidious.

413
00:26:19,960 --> 00:26:21,460
You must be in danger if you go there alone.

414
00:26:21,580 --> 00:26:22,480
Stay here and I’ll protect you.

415
00:26:22,580 --> 00:26:23,260
It doesn’t matter.

416
00:26:23,620 --> 00:26:24,920
I must go this time.

417
00:26:25,760 --> 00:26:27,240
She killed Rou Rou.

418
00:26:27,540 --> 00:26:29,000
I’ll avenge Rou Rou.

419
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:31,160
Ask my daddy to go there.

420
00:26:31,520 --> 00:26:32,600
I’ll try my best

421
00:26:32,660 --> 00:26:34,140
to let her admit her crime.

422
00:26:34,560 --> 00:26:35,120
In this case,

423
00:26:35,440 --> 00:26:37,100
we’ll gain the evidence to punish her.

424
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:39,540
OK.

425
00:26:40,540 --> 00:26:41,460
You must be careful.

426
00:26:50,940 --> 00:26:51,960
Immortal, please.

427
00:27:04,740 --> 00:27:05,740
Please.

428
00:27:30,700 --> 00:27:31,880
This way.

429
00:27:37,440 --> 00:27:38,100
Please.

430
00:27:41,700 --> 00:27:42,880
"Zifangyun Palace"
Please.

431
00:27:43,260 --> 00:27:45,840
As expected, it is Her Majesty.

432
00:28:55,900 --> 00:28:57,540
Fairy Jin Mi.

433
00:28:58,960 --> 00:28:59,480
No.

434
00:29:00,120 --> 00:29:02,640
I should call you Immortal Jin Mi now.

435
00:29:03,320 --> 00:29:05,420
I’ve been waiting for you for a long time.

436
00:29:16,520 --> 00:29:17,320
Xu Feng,

437
00:29:17,720 --> 00:29:18,980
it’s really lively today.

438
00:29:19,100 --> 00:29:20,200
It seems that we’re late.

439
00:29:21,520 --> 00:29:22,780
How lively it is!

440
00:29:22,860 --> 00:29:24,160
There’re so many immortals.

441
00:29:24,640 --> 00:29:26,540
Xu Feng, find a seat now.

442
00:29:27,760 --> 00:29:28,780
There is a seat.

443
00:29:28,940 --> 00:29:29,540
I’ll take it first.

444
00:29:43,740 --> 00:29:45,480
The discussion is very important today.

445
00:29:45,780 --> 00:29:47,280
Why isn’t Mother here?

446
00:29:48,020 --> 00:29:49,600
Your Majesty.

447
00:29:50,040 --> 00:29:52,300
I was going to ask Supreme Lord Lao for elixir.

448
00:29:52,500 --> 00:29:55,920
Unexpected, I was misled here
by the fairchild who didn’t know the way.

449
00:29:56,080 --> 00:29:57,520
I’m sorry for disturbing you.

450
00:29:57,660 --> 00:29:59,460
I’ll leave now.

451
00:30:17,860 --> 00:30:19,960
Jin Mi was taken away
by someone of Her Majesty.

452
00:30:33,460 --> 00:30:34,780
Where is Xu Feng?

453
00:30:41,560 --> 00:30:44,340
It’s true that we’ll make elixir today,

454
00:30:44,600 --> 00:30:48,220
but it isn’t like that of Supreme Lord Lao.

455
00:30:50,460 --> 00:30:52,500
I have wondered

456
00:30:53,140 --> 00:30:57,040
what your real body is.

457
00:30:57,800 --> 00:30:58,860
How about making elixir

458
00:30:59,100 --> 00:31:01,780
on this lucky day?

459
00:31:02,220 --> 00:31:04,520
So I’ll know more.

460
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:25,320
Your Majesty, please stop kidding.

461
00:31:26,100 --> 00:31:28,420
My daddy announced to all immortals that

462
00:31:28,860 --> 00:31:31,420
my real body is

463
00:31:31,560 --> 00:31:34,080
a Six-petal Frost Flower
in the Empyrean Cloud Palace that day.

464
00:31:34,320 --> 00:31:37,060
Demon Zi Fen

465
00:31:37,200 --> 00:31:40,300
did attract Water Immortal
with her beautiful appearance back then.

466
00:31:40,540 --> 00:31:43,540
However, no one knows who your daddy is.

467
00:31:43,860 --> 00:31:47,460
I think Even Water Immortal
can’t make sure of that.

468
00:31:47,780 --> 00:31:49,360
Words are but wind.

469
00:31:49,640 --> 00:31:51,920
No one has seen your real body so far.

470
00:31:52,180 --> 00:31:53,780
Seeing is believing.

471
00:31:54,340 --> 00:31:56,880
Let me check

472
00:31:57,260 --> 00:31:58,800
what you are actually today.

473
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:22,800
The hellfire can be divided into 8 levels.

474
00:32:23,040 --> 00:32:25,200
I think Firefly Fire, Candle Fire and Wood Fire

475
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:28,000
won’t work for you.

476
00:32:28,560 --> 00:32:30,560
Let’s start with the 4th level

477
00:32:31,140 --> 00:32:32,980
Alcohol-brewed Fire.

478
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:34,360
Back then,

479
00:32:35,280 --> 00:32:36,700
your mom

480
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:39,200
could stand the final level

481
00:32:39,260 --> 00:32:40,780
Glazed Pure Fire.

482
00:32:40,940 --> 00:32:43,700
I wonder which level you can stand.

483
00:32:44,440 --> 00:32:46,500
I fully expect that.

484
00:32:46,540 --> 00:32:47,740
That’s impossible.

485
00:32:48,540 --> 00:32:50,060
My mom was Floral Immortal.

486
00:32:50,440 --> 00:32:51,860
It was impossible for you to hurt her.

487
00:32:51,980 --> 00:32:54,020
She brought disaster to herself.

488
00:33:28,680 --> 00:33:30,660
I’m afraid you don’t

489
00:33:30,760 --> 00:33:32,380
mean to check my real body.

490
00:33:32,700 --> 00:33:33,700
I think

491
00:33:33,900 --> 00:33:35,920
you want to kill me here.

492
00:33:36,060 --> 00:33:38,260
You are quite clever.

493
00:33:39,160 --> 00:33:40,820
When I experienced hardships
in the mortal world back then,

494
00:33:40,820 --> 00:33:42,100
you sent someone to kill me.

495
00:33:42,680 --> 00:33:44,040
However, my good friend Rou Rou was killed,

496
00:33:44,100 --> 00:33:44,680
right?

497
00:33:44,860 --> 00:33:45,780
So what?

498
00:33:46,180 --> 00:33:47,860
You hurt my mom back then

499
00:33:48,640 --> 00:33:49,900
and killed my friend now.

500
00:33:50,320 --> 00:33:51,880
New hatred is piled on old.

501
00:33:51,960 --> 00:33:54,940
I’ll get even with you today.

502
00:33:56,080 --> 00:33:57,440
It’s impossible for you to do so.

503
00:34:34,260 --> 00:34:36,540
I’d better tell Run Yu first.

504
00:34:48,140 --> 00:34:50,620
Your Highness, Jin Mi is in danger.

505
00:34:54,220 --> 00:34:55,760
The 7th level of hellfire

506
00:34:56,240 --> 00:34:57,420
Boiling-oil Fire.

507
00:35:22,500 --> 00:35:24,380
You’re really Luo Lin’s daughter

508
00:35:24,540 --> 00:35:26,820
with such excellent water control power.

509
00:35:27,560 --> 00:35:28,900
Break.

510
00:35:41,240 --> 00:35:42,860
The 8th level of hellfire

511
00:35:43,020 --> 00:35:44,500
Glazed Pure Fire.

512
00:35:44,580 --> 00:35:45,380
Your Majesty,

513
00:35:46,840 --> 00:35:49,020
why must you kill me?

514
00:35:49,080 --> 00:35:51,480
Because you’re Zi Fen’s daughter

515
00:35:51,560 --> 00:35:53,780
with the similar appearance to her

516
00:35:53,860 --> 00:35:57,200
and you even dare to seduce my son.

517
00:35:57,360 --> 00:35:59,500
I must hold on and wait for my daddy.

518
00:36:02,500 --> 00:36:05,800
There is no regret that
you die for thousands of times.

519
00:36:06,100 --> 00:36:07,760
I didn’t expect that

520
00:36:07,980 --> 00:36:10,140
with the supreme power,

521
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:11,740
you were actually afraid of me.

522
00:36:12,420 --> 00:36:15,360
I’m so surprised.

523
00:36:15,540 --> 00:36:16,120
I’m afraid of you?

524
00:36:16,780 --> 00:36:18,300
I’m not afraid of you.

525
00:36:18,520 --> 00:36:20,340
If you’re not afraid of me,

526
00:36:20,940 --> 00:36:23,160
why do you only dare kill me with hellfire

527
00:36:23,360 --> 00:36:26,560
but not face up to me directly?

528
00:36:26,560 --> 00:36:27,480
You evildoer,

529
00:36:27,680 --> 00:36:30,180
I must kill you today.
